com.danielly.jsf.cinema.services

Class MovieDetails

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.danielly.jsf.cinema.services.MovieDetails
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Named
 @ViewScoped
public class MovieDetails
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Class MovieDetails is a service class that being used to get the details of the movie. When using the class we firstly set the movie id and than the onload gets the movie object. We are setting the parameters and loading with viewParam and viewAction in the web page. Once we loaded the the movie we can get the movie object.
